### Test Scenarios (Cases 1–15)
```
Case 1:  GET /api/v1/courses/stats → 200 { totalCourses, totalStudents, ... }
Case 2:  GET /api/v1/courses?page=0&size=12&search=cake&level=BEGINNER → 200 { content[], page, totalPages }
Case 4:  GET /api/v1/courses/slug/chocolate-cake-101 → 200 { id, title, curriculum, reviews }
Case 9:  GET /api/v1/subscriptions/plans → 200 [{ name: "Yearly", price: 1200 }]
Case 10: GET /api/v1/certificates/verify/CERT-2024-001 → 200 { valid, studentName, courseName }
```

