## 🔐 AUTHENTICATION (Cases 16–25)

| # | Feature | Status | Backend | Frontend                | Issues |
|---|---------|--------|---------|-------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|16 | Register| ✅     | `POST /api/v1/auth/register` → `AuthResponse` | [Register](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/feature-module/auth/register/register.tsx#30-559) component (561 lines) with password strength validation | None found |
| 17 | Email Verification | ✅ | `GET /api/v1/auth/verify-email?token=` | No dedicated frontend page — relies on email link hitting backend directly | ⚠️ No UI feedback page after verification; backend redirects unclear |
| 18 | Resend Verification | ⚠️ | `POST /api/v1/auth/resend-verification` exists in [AuthController](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/academy-backend/src/main/java/com/academy/controller/AuthController.java#19-108) | Not found in [auth.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/services/api/auth.service.ts) frontend API | 🐛 Backend endpoint exists but frontend doesn't call it |
| 19 | Login | ✅ | `POST /api/v1/auth/login` → `AuthResponse` | [Login](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/feature-module/auth/login/login.tsx#17-361) component dispatches `authSlice.login` thunk | None found |
| 20 | Forgot Password | ✅ | `POST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password` | `ForgortPassword` component (typo in filename) | None found |
| 21 | Reset Password | ✅ | `POST /api/v1/auth/reset-password` | `SetPassword` component at `/set-password` route | None found |
| 22 | Token Refresh | ✅ | `POST /api/v1/auth/refresh-token` | Axios response interceptor auto-refreshes on 401 | None found |
| 23 | Logout | ✅ | `POST /api/v1/auth/logout` | `authService.logout()` clears localStorage | ⚠️ Backend invalidates refresh token but access token remains valid until expiry (no server-side blacklist) |
| 24 | Protected Routes | ⚠️ | Backend: [SecurityConfig](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/academy-backend/src/main/java/com/academy/config/SecurityConfig.java#23-99) requires auth for `/api/v1/**` except public endpoints | [SubscriptionGuard](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/feature-module/common/SubscriptionGuard.tsx#10-29) only checks [isAuthenticated](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/services/api/auth.service.ts#85-89) from Redux state | 🐛 Guard only checks Redux state — if user manually navigates and Redux isn't hydrated, guard may fail. Also, instructor/admin routes have NO frontend guard at all. |
| 25 | Role Guard | ❌ | Backend: `@PreAuthorize("hasRole('ADMIN')")` on [AdminController](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/academy-backend/src/main/java/com/academy/controller/AdminController.java#15-143), `@PreAuthorize("hasAnyRole('INSTRUCTOR', 'ADMIN')")` on [InstructorController](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/academy-backend/src/main/java/com/academy/controller/InstructorController.java#19-309) | **No role-based guards** in frontend routing | 🐛 Student can navigate to `/instructor/*` or `/admin/*` routes — they'll see the UI but API calls will fail with 403. Bad UX. |

### Key Issues Found
> [!WARNING]
> **Case 25**: No frontend role-based route guards exist. All dashboard routes (student, instructor, admin) are registered as `publicRoutes` in [router.link.tsx](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/feature-module/router/router.link.tsx). Only the [SubscriptionGuard](file:///c:/Users/asus/Documents/Project%20main/plateforme/template/src/feature-module/common/SubscriptionGuard.tsx#10-29) (auth check) wraps student pages. Instructor and admin pages have **zero** frontend protection.

